  "text": "Essentially, BL21 DE3 competent bacteria (Stratagene) were transformed with pGEX plasmids. Single colonies were picked and grown in 2YT media. Expression of GST-fusion proteins was induced with 0.01mM IPTG for 2.5 hours at 37°C, cells were collected and lysed in buffer (50mM Tris-Cl pH 7.5, 150mM NaCl, 0.05% NP-40). Recombinant protein were batch purified using glutathione-sepharose beads. GST-SETD6 was purified similarly, but from Sf9 insect cells as described [CITATION_1] .",
